<sect3>
<title>Checkout commands for developers</title>

<para>
Developers need the following commands to checkout the whole source tree:
</para>

<informalexample>
  <screen>
svn co svn+ssh://svn.debian.org/svn/d-i/trunk debian-installer
cd debian-installer
scripts/git-setup
mr -p checkout
  </screen>
</informalexample>
</sect3>

